---
title: The 'Rachel' Chicken Sammie with Slaw and Pickle
description: Toasted buns get piled high with spiced chicken tenders, slaw and cheddar cheese. A slather of mayo and a side of potato wedges make this diner classic a family favourite. Pass the cherry coke!
